kpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/Th%E1%BB%A9-C%C3%BAc-Pha-t%E1%BA%B7ng-thi/poem-gxa3FX0q9ruPHHzMRC6NJw">Thứ Cúc Pha tặng thi - 次菊坡贈詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-H%E1%BA%A3i-V%C3%A2n-quan/poem-UoH1ab6bERZRYd0yd0oBbg">Thướng Hải Vân quan - 上海雲關</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%B4ng-V%C5%A9-sinh-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-VDPbM6HbzyGfnLNl6bn0NQ">Tông Vũ sinh nhật - 宗武生日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%C3%A3n-ph%E1%BB%91-quy-ph%C3%A0m/poem-buAyaYlGOcEcwRhKgFS1fQ">Vãn phố quy phàm - 晚浦歸帆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
